reviewText:
To make long story short:
1) Aura that can only be understood by players from post-soviet states:
2) 13 possible endings;
3) All the characters are just awesome and unique;
4) Anime style is somehow charming;
5) Storyline is very detailed.
Conclusion: 10/10. Game that partially broke my heart and motivated to make some changes in my life.
P.S. Alisa is the best IMHO. I can say that i fell in love.

